WEBVTT

00:02:58.960 --> 00:03:00.736
what can one type to find out?

00:03:00.760 --> 00:03:05.056
Very often children ask their parents,

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:09.296
“What building is this?"
Or "Who is this person on TV?"

00:03:09.320 --> 00:03:10.840
Or “Which flower is this?”

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:15.416
I would like to remind you

00:03:15.450 --> 00:03:18.983
that 781 million people
cannot read or write,

00:03:19.007 --> 00:03:22.496
which is about 15 percent
of the world’s population.

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:27.616
Yet the entire internet is based on words.

00:03:28.320 --> 00:03:33.160
Imagine, if you could get information
on whatever you see,